nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Cinematic 8K footage, photorealistic style with high visual consistency.
Scene & Subject:
In a cozy, sun-drenched urban cafe, a young East Asian woman with long, wavy dark hair sits at a wooden table. She wears a beige shirt over a white top and blue jeans. Sunlight filters through the window, casting warm glows.
Text Rendering & Object Detail:
She holds a matte black ceramic coffee mug with both hands. On the front of the mug facing the camera, the text "ComfyUI ì˜¤ë½ì‹¤" is clearly printed in elegant white bold font. The text renders with high fidelity, perfectly curved along the cylindrical surface of the mug.
Action & Fluid Motion:
The woman performs a smooth, continuous action: she gently lifts the mug to her lips for a slow sip. As the mug moves and tilts, the text "ComfyUI ì˜¤ë½ì‹¤" remains fixed to the surface, following the object's perspective and rotation naturally without distortion. She then lowers the cup, revealing the text again, while smiling softly at the window.
Physics & Lighting:
Realistically generated steam rises from the coffee, wafting past the text. The ambient golden light reflects subtly off the ceramic texture and the white lettering, integrating the text into the physical environment.
Camera Movement:
A slow dolly-in shot focuses on the mug and her expression, ensuring the text remains legible and sharp throughout the movement.
Aesthetics:
Warm autumn color grading, shallow depth of field blurring the background, maintaining a coherent and high-quality cinematic look.
